# CDK TypeScript Project Commands

## Development
build: npm run build
watch: npm run watch
test: npm test
test:watch: npm run test -- --watch
lint: npm run eslint
typecheck: npx tsc --noEmit

## CDK Commands
synth: npx cdk synth
deploy: npx cdk deploy
destroy: npx cdk destroy
diff: npx cdk diff
list: npx cdk list
bootstrap: npx cdk bootstrap

## CDK with specific stack
deploy-stack: npx cdk deploy $1
destroy-stack: npx cdk destroy $1
synth-stack: npx cdk synth $1

## Utilities
clean: rm -rf cdk.out node_modules && npm install
deps: npm install
update: npm update
audit: npm audit
fix: npm audit fix

## Documentation
docs: npx typedoc